reviewText: This 6 disc set takes a look back at some of the great international stars who graced ECW rings over the years. From Rey Mysterio Jr., Psicosis, and Juventud Guerrera to Masato Tanaka, Taka Michinoku, and Great Sasuke, they're all here. This is an RF Video release, and picture quality can vary here and there, as these were recorded off TV and not the master tapes, which WWE owns. The matches involving Tanaka, Super Crazy, and Yoshihiro Tajiri are the real highlights Worth a look.
